{"tid":2120444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"組織罷課名校仔DSE報捷料讀港大法律： 抗爭是持久戰「十幾廿年都未打完」","createTime":"2020-07-22T16:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T23:20:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ba94dd02e34b365bf82f23e79af78113777cdace","tid":2120444,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/ZAM2W4KZWE6XM3FZB7UF2WA62U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FZAM2W4KZWE6XM3FZB7UF2WA62U%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgAfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=5c90b29d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FZAM2W4KZWE6XM3FZB7UF2WA62U%2F&h=69a0c257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/ZAM2W4KZWE6XM3FZB7UF2WA62U/</a><br />\n<br />\n反修例⼀波未平，疫情即至，《港區國安法》一波又起。應屆文憑試考生經歷了艱難的一年，曾組織聖保羅書院同學罷課的劉建希（Desmond）卻考得最佳五科29分佳績，預計可順利入讀心儀的港大文學士與法律學雙學位課程。立志讀法律捍衞香港核心價值的Desmond斥《港區國安法》條文是「DSE就算中文唔合格都寫得出」，雖然香港法治情況惡劣，但暫不考慮移民。他指這場抗爭是持久戰，要先裝備自己，「好多人都同我哋依屆學生講，依場仗唔好以為兩三年⋯⋯十幾廿年都未打完」。"},{"pid":"7d5c1d24d5de533a2ea0be1a3b721bfb1b7afaa1","tid":2120444,"uid":293227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"DSE手足加油"},{"pid":"50ef213d74c886142c980ebf281e3f5829844e8b","tid":2120444,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"3cc8ce3ae54189f1a23559ca9bcf3ecf44d82dee","tid":2120444,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T16:48:39.000Z","msg":"收聲呀，冇人想知呀，神獸靜靜雞呀，收聲啦"},{"pid":"5f662b317291a710d44fcaaf9b0b9b3b17777b48","tid":2120444,"uid":258109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebef15b50025d04288e0e5b4886857327443be3","tid":2120444,"uid":232157,"